name: Softball Training- Level I
description: Basic softball-specific training for coaches and athletes.  Includes on-field warm-ups, shoulder prehab exercises, core workouts, speed and quickness drills and strength circuits.  Everything can be done on the field with minimal equipment.  Video clips for every exercise.  Printable workout sheets and nutrition handouts.  A must-have for every softball coach!

name: Hockey Dryland Training I
description: HOCKEY I is perfect for players who are new to off-ice training. This program builds a solid foundation in all areas of athleticism- hockey mobility, hockey stability, hockey speed, hockey strength and hockey stamina. Conditioning workouts are included. Workouts are performed 2-4 times each week, depending on the phase of training, and can be completed with 4 inexpensive pieces of equipment- a medicine ball, stability ball, ankle band, and resistance cord. Also included: a hockey-specific testing plan for assessing strengths and weaknesses and monitoring progress, and an extensive performance nutrition section.

name: Hockey Dryland Training II
description: HOCKEY II is for serious players who have a minimum of 2 years of off-ice training. This program focuses on the critical aspects of on-ice performance: acceleration speed, quickness, agility, lower body power, total body strength, and hockey-specific conditioning. A supplemental goalie-specific section is included that addresses goalie reaction time, goalie lateral quickness, goalie mobility and goalie stamina. Equipment needs include a medicine ball, stability ball, ankle band, resistance cord, dumbbells, Bosu Trainer and slideboard (optional). HOCKEY II also includes an evaluation plan and detailed performance nutrition section. **Coaches interested in integrating off-ice training can learn hundreds of hockey-specific exercises & drills for warm-ups & workouts.

name: Core Performance Training
description: ATHLETE CONSTRUCTION’s CORE STRENGTH DVD is a comprehensive core training program designed for athletes of all ages and abilities. The 36-week program progresses you through 12 exercise levels. Workouts train the core the way it is used in sport and everyday life! A combination of stabilization exercises, rotation exercises, flexion exercises and lateral flexion exercises are incorporated to develop superior form and function. The entire program can be completed with a stability ball.

name: Soccer Training I
description: This soccer training program is a great resource for soccer coaches and soccer athletes. Built on a foundation of mobility, core stabilization strength and work capacity, it progressively increases soccer speed, strength and stamina. This comprehensive 18-week training program requires minimal equipment, but guarantees maximum results. It includes daily workouts, an athlete evaluation protocol and a detailed performance nutrition section. Print the daily workout sheet, watch the exercise clips for each drill and exercise in the workout, and you’re ready to go! Workouts require a medicine ball, stability ball, resistance cord &/or dumbbells, AND THAT’S IT!

name: Fueling Like A Champion
description: This DVD leaves no stone left unturned, as Dr. Mohr and Mitzi reveal the absolute best nutrition secrets young athletes need to reach their true potential! From sports drinks to eating while traveling, protein needs to recovery nutrition--we uncover the truth and the absolute most up to date scientific recommendations to unleash the true potential of your athletes in every single area of performance nutrition! If you owned a multi-million dollar race horse, would you feed it sugar, chips, junk foods, soft drinks, and not feed it breakfast before it raced? NOT A CHANCE! Then why is it any different for young athletes, who are trying to perform at their best both physically and mentally? Learn to fuel their bodies with high octane, super high nutrient foods and fluids that will ultimately allow them to be the very best they can be! Young athletes are faced with many demands—from long travel, multiple practices, or simply hours on end in school before they even get on the field—learn how to handle every unique situation with the ‘Fuel Like a Champion’ DVD. In Fuel Like a Champion - A Young Athlete's Guide on What to Eat, the experts uncover: 1. The potential dangers of Energy Drinks—there are over SIX HUNDRED brands literally preying on false hopes and dreams of young athletes--and your kids are drinking them! 2. The exact, science-based carbohydrate recommendations to guarantee more energy on and off the field! 3. The specific protein requirements to ensure optimal muscle growth and recovery 4. The truth behind the $16.8 billion dietary supplement industry…trust us, with over 29,000 dietary supplements available, you NEED this information to save your young athlete from falling prey to marketing hype! 5. Recovery strategies -- breakthrough recovery strategies that will take performance to the next level! 6. Guidance on safe, effective, and permanent weight loss 7. Precise, healthy, and LEGAL weight gain strategies guaranteed to pack on muscle and strength (for those who want it) 8. Exact food recommendations to meet the exact requirements for developing athletes 9. The top 12 fruits and vegetables to buy organic—they are otherwise highest in pesticides, so you need to protect you and your young athletes! 10. Specific nutrient timing strategies teaching you when and what to eat before and during games. 11. The best times to consume sports drinks and when they’re nothing more than extra calories—this information can make or break performance! And much, much more Purchase HERE!

name: Grocery Shopping Made Easy
description: Let's face it - every nutrition decision you make starts in the grocery store. And if you don't know what foods to choose...and which to lose, you will continue to struggle in achieving that lean, healthy body you've desired. The Grocery Shopping Made Easy DVD does exactly what it says - it makes the otherwise cumbersome process of shopping EASY and teaches you how to feed your body to lose fat, gain health and lean muscle, or whatever your goals are...permanently! It shows you how REAL people can use a more effective shopping experience to transform themselves! If you look in the mirror and are not happy with your body, then it's time to do something different. And if you're not happy, ask yourself "Why not?" * Are you unsure of what it takes to lose weight? * Do you struggle with making exercise permanent? * Are you confused with all the misinformation force fed to you through the media? All of these could be true, but you know what---the foods you eat (or don't eat) are holding you back from permanent weight loss success! Imagine, for one moment, that you could become leaner, healthier, stronger, and have more energy permanently...but only if you knew the information covered on this DVD, including: * THE #1 secret to grocery shopping that will make or break your efforts...few people know this! * How to avoid tricks that marketers use tomake you hungrier to buy their food, even if it's not what you want to buy (Hint: fast food companies do the same thing); * HOW to read a food label, keying in on ingredients that will enhance your body transformation...and others that can sabotage your goals; * How "healthy" salad bars can backfire and cause weight gain! * The truth about organic foods - are they all that they are cracked up to be? And much, much more... Purchase HERE!
